---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={"Identité, Style et Sous-cultures | " + SITE_TITLE} description="Identité, Style et Sous-cultures category page" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main class="category-page" style="width: 75%; max-width: none; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <header style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h1>Identité, Style et Sous-cultures</h1>
        </header>

        <section class="category-article" style="margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
            <p>Au-delà des métaux, le bijou est un uniforme de l'âme. Cette dimension explore comment les styles — du gothique au minimalisme — servent de codes de reconnaissance sociale. Le Choker, par exemple, a voyagé de la noblesse aux rébellions punks. Nous analysons ici le bijou comme un outil de différenciation et d'appartenance. Ce texte de pont établit que le choix d'un style est un acte politique et esthétique qui définit la place de l'individu. En comprenant les codes des sous-cultures, le lecteur apprend que porter un bijou est une narration visuelle, un moyen de signaler ses valeurs et ses révoltes sans prononcer un seul mot.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="category-wp-content">
<figure class="wp-block-uagb-image__figure"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/media-images/posts/styles-et-identit-sociale-illustration-1.webp" alt="Illustration for Identité, Style et Sous-cultures" class="uag-image-1358" width="1200" height="350" title="Identité, Style et Sous-cultures" role="img"></figure>
</section>



        



<section class="category-keywords" style="margin: 40px 0; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.3rem;">Related Keywords</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;">
        <a href="/blog/signification-collier-choker-histoire/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #9335B6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#signification collier choker histoire</a>
        <a href="/blog/bijoux-gothiques-symbolisme-evolution/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #9335B6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#bijoux gothiques symbolisme</a>
        <a href="/blog/tendance-bijoux-minimalistes/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #9335B6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#tendance bijoux minimalistes</a>
        <a href="/blog/boho-chic-jewelry-evolution/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #9335B6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#look bijoux bohème chic</a>
        <a href="/blog/piercing-oreille-odyssee-culturelle-2/" class="keyword-btn active" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: var(--accent, #9335B6); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: opacity 0.2s;">#piercing oreille signification culturelle</a>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="category-faq-section" style="margin-top: 60px; padding: 40px 30px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea;">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #222222; font-size: 2rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-content" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Pourquoi le Choker est-il iconique ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Il oscille entre servitude et haute mode.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Bijoux gothiques symbolisme ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Beauté dans l'obscurité et memento mori.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Minimalisme en joaillerie ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Focus sur l'essence et la pureté.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Bijoux Punk et rébellion ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Détournement d'objets usuels (épingles).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Signification du piercing ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Marqueur culturel ou rite moderne.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
